        Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Aenean eu leo quam.
        Pellentesque ornare sem lacinia.
      </p>

      <!-- ------- Bloc 1 ------- -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <!-- Titre 1 -->
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Pellentesque</h3>
          <!-- Texte 1 -->
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center font-light">Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
