          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Inceptos</h3>
          <!-- Texte 2 -->
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center font-light">Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <!-- Titre 3 -->
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Vehicula</h3>
          <!-- Texte  3-->
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center font-light">Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ------- Forme 4 - Image à droite ------- -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 p-10 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <!-- Titre -->
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Vestibulum Magna</h2>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="bg-beige h-1 w-32 rounded"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Texte -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-light">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod
            tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam,
            quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
